.Vb 3
\& my $rv = Net::SSLeay::SESSION_new();
\& #
\& # returns: value corresponding to openssl\*(Aqs SSL_SESSION structure (0 on failure)
.Ve
.IP "\(bu" 4
SESSION_free
.Sp
Free an allocated \s-1SSL_SESSION\s0 structure.
.Sp
.Vb 4
\& Net::SSLeay::SESSION_free($ses);
