.Ve
.Sp
Check openssl doc <http://www.openssl.org/docs/ssl/SSL_SESSION_free.html>
.IP "\(bu" 4
SESSION_cmp
.Sp
Compare two \s-1SSL_SESSION\s0 structures.
.Sp
.Vb 5
\& my $rv = Net::SSLeay::SESSION_cmp($sesa, $sesb);
