SESSION_set_ex_data
.Sp
Is used to store application data at arg for idx into the session object.
.Sp
.Vb 6
\& my $rv = Net::SSLeay::SESSION_set_ex_data($ss, $idx, $data);
\& # $ss \- value corresponding to openssl\*(Aqs SSL_SESSION structure
\& # $idx \- (integer) ???
