.Sp
\&\fB\s-1COMPATIBILITY:\s0\fR not available in Net\-SSLeay\-1.45 and before
.Sp
Returns \s-1ASN1_OBJECT\s0 corresponding to X509 certificate public key algorithm.
.Sp
.Vb 4
\& my $rv = Net::SSLeay::P_X509_get_pubkey_alg($x);
