Returns the \s-1SSL BIO\s0 method. This is a filter \s-1BIO\s0 which is a wrapper
round the OpenSSL \s-1SSL\s0 routines adding a \s-1BIO \s0'flavour' to \s-1SSL I/O.\s0
.Sp
